      <title>法国极右翼政党趋向组建联盟对抗马克龙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/french-far-right-parties-edge-toward-coalition-against-macron</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国极右翼领导人玛丽娜·勒庞领导的国民联盟党与议员马里恩·马雷夏尔目前正在就联手在即将举行的立法选举中对抗法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的可能性进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/french-far-right-parties-edge-toward-coalition-against-macron</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 17:33:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示，勒庞领导的政党在法国大选中以 34% 领先</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/le-pen-s-party-seen-leading-with-34-in-french-election-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项民意调查显示，在即将举行的法国立法选举第一轮投票中，极右翼领导人玛丽娜·勒庞领导的国民联盟预计将获得 34% 的选民意向，而总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙领导的执政党的支持率仅为 19%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/le-pen-s-party-seen-leading-with-34-in-french-election-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 17:32:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新对手崛起后，奥尔班排除提前举行匈牙利选举的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/orban-rules-out-early-hungary-elections-after-new-rival-s-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于新对手表现意外强劲，匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班排除了提前举行议会选举的可能性，以巩固其在地方和欧盟选举中的优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/orban-rules-out-early-hungary-elections-after-new-rival-s-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 17:20:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默副手恢复布莱尔时代减少英国无家可归者的方法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/uk-election-starmer-deputy-angela-rayner-channels-blair-to-cut-homelessness</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果反对党在下个月的大选中赢得权力，工党副领袖安吉拉·雷纳 (Angela Rayner) 计划建立一个新的公务员部门来推动消除无家可归现象，这将借鉴前首相托尼·布莱尔 (Tony Blair) 曾经使用过的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/uk-election-starmer-deputy-angela-rayner-channels-blair-to-cut-homelessness</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:47:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国对胡塞武装石油运输实施新制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/us-imposes-fresh-sanctions-targeting-houthi-oil-shipments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国宣布对 10 名个人、船只和公司实施制裁，旨在切断也门胡塞叛军的商品收入，胡塞叛军多次袭击商业航运商，扰乱了红海的贸易流通。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/us-imposes-fresh-sanctions-targeting-houthi-oil-shipments</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:36:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>根据众议院计划，美国和以色列将进行年度隧道演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/us-israel-would-conduct-annual-tunnel-exercises-under-house-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院军事委员会最新的8950亿美元国防开支法案草案将要求美国与以色列举行联合演习，旨在提高两国打击地下隧道武装分子和走私者的能力，这是对抗哈马斯和其他组织的关键优势的举措之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/us-israel-would-conduct-annual-tunnel-exercises-under-house-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:16:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克人指责俄罗斯支持布拉格未遂纵火袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/czechs-blame-russia-for-backing-failed-arson-attack-in-prague</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克共和国指责俄罗斯组织并资助上周一名外国人在布拉格试图纵火焚烧公共汽车但未遂的纵火事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/czechs-blame-russia-for-backing-failed-arson-attack-in-prague</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:07:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟选举加剧政治风险 新兴货币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/emerging-currencies-drop-as-eu-elections-add-to-political-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，大多数新兴市场货币兑美元走弱，波动性指标跳升，因欧洲大选中极右翼势力崛起导致政治风险成为焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/emerging-currencies-drop-as-eu-elections-add-to-political-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 10:51:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨在德国东部选举中再次遭遇惨败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/scholz-heading-for-another-election-debacle-in-eastern-germany</link>
      <description><![CDATA[9 月份，德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的执政联盟似乎将再次遭遇惨败。届时，德国东部三个地区将举行选举，而极右翼德国选择党是这三个地区最强大的政党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/scholz-heading-for-another-election-debacle-in-eastern-germany</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 08:50:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利新贵崛起，奥尔班的坚不可摧被打破</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/orban-ekes-out-win-in-hungary-s-eu-vote-as-challenger-surges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新晋政治家彼得·马扎尔 (Peter Magyar) 在欧洲议会选举中飙升至第二位，打破了匈牙利作为除了总理维克托·奥尔班 (Viktor Orban) 的统治之外别无选择的国家的形象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/orban-ekes-out-win-in-hungary-s-eu-vote-as-challenger-surges</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 21:34:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
